Finally, 'Uncle' Moody Awori writes about himself. Riding on a Tiger is a narrative of numerous historical intrigues that every reader wishes to know. The official launch of the book was on Tuesday at the Michael Joseph auditorium.Many prominent people came to witness and support the former Vice President.In attendance were Safaricom CEO Bob Collymore, Bidco CEO Vimal Shah, businessman Joe Wanjui, among others.